@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
    ViewBag.Title = "About Drip Smart USA – Precision Irrigation Leaders";
}

<section class="page-hero" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0e1438 0%, #181F4E 100%);">
    <div class="container page-hero-inner">
        <div class="page-hero-text">
            <nav class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / <span>About Us</span></nav>
            <h1>60 Years of Making<br/>Every Drop Count</h1>
            <p>From a small farm in the American Southwest to a nationwide network of growers — our mission has never changed: empower every farmer to grow more with less.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Mission -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="two-col-layout">
            <div>
                <span class="section-eyebrow">Our Mission</span>
                <h2>Precision Irrigation for Every Farmer, Everywhere</h2>
                <p>We believe that the best way to feed a growing world is to farm smarter — not larger. For over six decades, we've dedicated ourselves to building irrigation technology that makes every drop of water count.</p>
                <p style="margin-top:14px;">That means studying how each crop actually drinks, how soils actually move water, and how growers actually operate — and engineering components that reflect that reality precisely.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-stat-card" style="align-self:start;">
                <div class="big-stat"><span class="big-number">1965</span><span class="big-label">Founded</span></div>
                <div class="big-stat"><span class="big-number">10K+</span><span class="big-label">Farms Served</span></div>
                <div class="big-stat"><span class="big-number">50</span><span class="big-label">US States</span></div>
                <div class="big-stat"><span class="big-number">60+</span><span class="big-label">Years of R&D</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Values -->
<section class="section" style="background:var(--green-pale);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header centered">
            <span class="section-eyebrow">What Drives Us</span>
            <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="three-col-grid">
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon"><i data-lucide="globe"></i></div>
                <h3>Sustainability</h3>
                <p>We engineer every product to preserve water, reduce chemical inputs, and protect the land for future generations of farmers.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon"><i data-lucide="handshake"></i></div>
                <h3>Grower-First Design</h3>
                <p>Every specification, material choice, and feature we build starts with a single question: does this make the grower's season easier, more profitable, and more water-efficient?</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon"><i data-lucide="microscope"></i></div>
                <h3>Innovation</h3>
                <p>Our R&D team continuously pushes the boundaries of irrigation science — from anti-siphon emitter technology to AI-powered fertigation algorithms in DripSphere OS™.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Sustainability -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px; text-align:center;">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">Sustainability</span>
        <h2>Profitability and Sustainability Are the Same Thing</h2>
        <p style="margin-top:12px;">The most water-efficient farm is also the most profitable farm. The most nutrient-efficient crop is also the healthiest crop. At Drip Smart USA, we've never seen sustainability and business success as competing goals — they're inseparable.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:14px;">Our ReGen Recycling program closes the loop entirely — used driplines are collected, recycled, and turned into new driplines. Zero waste, full circle.</p>
        <a href="/recycling" class="btn-primary mt-md">Learn About ReGen Recycling</a>
    </div>
</section>
